[SN]TITLE[SN]
Armed police called to Aberdare incident

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Armed police have been sent to Aberdare as officers deal with an incident reported to involve threats being made with a firearm.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said armed officers had been dispatched "as a precaution".
No more details have been given and the incident is ongoing.
